 res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><h3>4.FIIL T1 XS 真无线运动耳机</h3><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2808124"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="万字长文：真无线蓝牙耳机选购指南！五款主流产品全方位对比评测" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd992e26b3f62835.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">FIILT1XS真无线蓝牙无线运动耳机苹果华为小米通用陶瓷白<strong class="price res_smzdm">289元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><h3>5.mifo o7 真无线运动蓝牙耳机</h3><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2808127"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="万字长文：真无线蓝牙耳机选购指南！五款主流产品全方位对比评测" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd99317527d78976.png_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">魔浪O7动铁真无线蓝牙耳机TWS入耳式运动防水双耳超小迷你隐形耳塞苹果安卓华为手机通用深灰色/单频动铁<strong class="price res_smzdm">499元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; display: inline !important;"> </span></span></span></span></span></dir><h3>外观</h3><p itemprop="description">5款耳机均是入耳耳机，都有大小多套硅胶耳套配送，选择合适的耳套有不小的物理降噪加成。外观设计上，除了FIIL的两款类似并且是按照运动耳机的方向在走位，其他比较起来都有各自的特色，很难说谁好谁坏，看个人喜欢了。</p><p itemprop="description">FunBuds ，烟灰粉、雾霾蓝、雪映白三种配色。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a4wog43l/pic_28/' target='_blank'><img alt="万字长文：真无线蓝牙耳机选购指南！五款主流产品全方位对比评测" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd9a2ab5ed7e2531.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='http