ription">《萌宠视察图》</p><p itemprop="description">机箱通常是她跳上隔壁架子的阶梯<img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/23.png" class="face" /></p><p itemprop="description">这个硬盘架子需要拧螺丝下来，硬盘固定方式也是拧螺丝，觉得不是很方便。怎么不上抽屉式的架子呢？<img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/27.png" class="face" /></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a07npn7r/pic_22/' target='_blank'><img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc368acd06b3866.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">螺丝有五种，但是混在一起的，没有分开包装</p><p itemprop="description">怎么说呢</p><p itemprop="description">不是很方便吧</p><p itemprop="description">而且容易滑丝</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a07npn7r/pic_23/' target='_blank'><img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/18/5fdc371b0a6b48225.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a07npn7r/pic_24/' target='_blank'><img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc371b490d01927.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><h2 id="cl_4">完工</h2><p itemprop="description">一开始开不了机</p><p itemprop="description">拔下内存擦擦插上就好了<img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/28.png" class="face" /><img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/28.png" class="face" /><img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/28.png" class="face" /></p><p itemprop="description">这究竟是科学还是玄学？</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a07npn7r/pic_25/' target='_blank'><img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc3847a24b52377.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a07npn7r/pic_26/' target='_blank'><img alt="￼￼机箱升级-九州风神魔方110白色版" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc3847cf8837584.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">有显卡支架</p><p itemprop="descri