s://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb636f386762302.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">华硕ROG STRIX ARION移动固态硬盘盒属于华硕的信仰系列外设装备，主打个性和高性能。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_22/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb636f6c0544852.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_23/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb636fa4c883984.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">除了酷炫外观，还有RGB灯效加持。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_24/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb636f5a74a3395.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">开箱，还附带了挂装套件。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_25/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb636fdd90e7430.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_26/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb636ff382b5070.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">ROG STRIX ARION移动固态硬盘盒附带了A TO C和C TO C两条数据线，满足了日常的所有应用场景。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_27/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6370390671615.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/yidongyingpanhe/" target="_blank">移动硬盘盒</a>像一个扁平的钥匙扣一样，采用了黑色的金属材质，大面积平行纹理造型很有质感。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_28/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb63707039e3338.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">上部有RGB发光灯带</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_29/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6370a4a239544.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">下部有钥匙持扣，方便携带</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_30/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6370c5c361727.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">硬盘盒背面是黑色的科幻线条风格，上部有ROG信仰LOGO</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_31/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6370dccf82728.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">移动固态硬盘盒侧面</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_32/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb63713fe792170.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">打开硬盘盒</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_33/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6371627679399.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_34/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6371bf086557.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">硬盘盒的上壳体<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_35/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6371b574b4944.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">硬盘盒安装SSD的位置</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_36/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb63722ef10557.jpg_e