02012/17/5fdb6373441b4607.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">A2000全貌</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_45/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/17/5fdb63739dc5b7486.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_46/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6373be3376290.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_47/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6373c30914704.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">A2000的主控采用了SMI2263ENG主控<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_48/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb637433a659794.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">缓存颗粒进行了二次封装，刻蚀有金士顿LOGO。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_49/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb637442b39376.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">存储颗粒来自镁光，型号为9SB2DNW951，经过查询是96层TLC颗粒。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_50/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb63744ca6d6994.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><h2 id="cl_2">三、进行测试</h2><p itemprop="description">1、理论测试</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_51/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6771c4d081696.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">接下来将A2000接入系统从盘，现在进行性能测试。</p><p itemprop="description">1G样本容量</p><p itemprop="description">AS SSD Benchmark</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_52/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6771e2c833932.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">ATTO disk benchmarks</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_53/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6771c835f1088.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">CrystalDiskMark</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_54/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb67724a31c5181.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">TXBench</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_55/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb67725b3b88598.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">将ROG STRIX ARION移动固态硬盘与SSD组合安装</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_56/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb6374bd8839941.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_57/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb637530f082127.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">将手机插上U盘进行数据读取，ROG灯亮起。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_58/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb67b6d5bb74762.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_59/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/17/5fdb67b76deaf2382.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/