itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4wqg3/pic_67/' target='_blank'><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb68573bde34300.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">移动SSD中存放游戏，日常应用或者大型游戏读写，也没有掉速、卡顿等问题。</p><h2 id="cl_3">四、总结</h2><p itemprop="description">曾经的双卡手机，TF卡和NANO SIM卡可以2选1。而现在，越来越多的手机已经放弃了TF卡槽，进入5G时代，越来越多的手机越来越重，没有了TF卡的手机只能通过手机的OTG功能，来实现低成本扩容，特别是用来存储影音资料非常靠谱。而自己DIY一块中意的移动SSD，除了速度，更是一种个性的选择。</p><p itemprop="description">商品连接</p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2811080"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb68f865aed8743.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">【至高减650】realme真我X7Pro天玑1000+120Hz柔性屏6400万广角四摄5g手机官方旗舰店青春学生拍照大屏轻薄<strong class="price res_smzdm">2399元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">天猫精选</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2811077"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="TF卡槽终被抛弃一5G手机到底如何扩容？" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdb68c0682f14188.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">华硕（ASUS）ROG幻影STRIXARION高速M2硬盘盒支持固态硬盘移动外接ROG标准版<strong class="price res_smzdm">399元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2811076"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img