<p itemprop="description">餐厨狭小多个人就转不开身，收纳空间也是捉襟见肘。什么是既能满足收纳又能让出过道，让空间有空可言的好东西？小编今儿个就来说说平时可能不大会关注的—缝隙柜。</p><p itemprop="description">为什么会突然想起说这个呢，我真的是一个特别喜欢塞东西的人，哪有缝塞哪，搞得整个家里缝隙处时不时就炸出一个购物袋子，就很难看，既然喜欢用缝隙，就不如买个能塞进去的<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/yigui/" target="_blank">柜子</a>，岂不是更好？</p><p itemprop="description">门后的缝隙可以选这种不到20cm的缝隙柜，轻松收纳几十双鞋，还不占空间。 </p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a4wo0l97/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="每日好物：犄角旮旯的缝隙柜，小编帮你找了这几款，让捉襟见肘的空间有空可言！" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc71d38159c946.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="120586"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2812673"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="每日好物：犄角旮旯的缝隙柜，小编帮你找了这几款，让捉襟见肘的空间有空可言！" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc716c186d5836.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">入户新中式超薄鞋柜换鞋凳一体17CM实木翻斗式门口窄家用省空间<strong class="price res_smzdm">1070元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">天猫精选</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2812682"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="每日好物：犄角旮旯的缝隙柜，小编帮你找了这几款，让捉襟见肘的空间有空可言！" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc71877c709106.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">鞋柜超薄窄家用门口实木框大容量入户小翻斗式简约现代门厅柜17cm<strong class="price res_smzdm">¥ 693.63-1356.46</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">天猫精选</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2812685"><span class="embed-card main-site res_sm